quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  26,160,Ummanni Luuxis ergamoota sobsiifte
  26,161,"Yeroo obboleessi isaanii Luux isaanin jedhu: “Sila Rabbiin hin sodaattanii"
  26,162,"Dhugumatti, ani isiniif ergamaa amanamaadha"
  26,163,Rabbiin sodaadhaa; ergaa kiyyas fudhaa
  26,164,Ani isa (waamicha kana) irratti mindaa tokkollee isin hin gaafadhuMindaan kiyya Gooftaa aalama hundaa irra malee hin taane
  26,165,Sila isin (qunnamtii saalaatiif) aalama hunda irraa dhiirotatti dhuftuu
  26,166,"Waan Gooftaan keessan haadhotii manaa keessan irraa isiniif uumes ni dhiiftuu? Dhugumatti isin ummata daangaa dabritoota” [jedhe]"
  26,167,"[Isaan] ni jedhan: “Yaa Luux! Yoo [waan jettu irraa] hin dhorgamin, dhugumatti warra [biyyarraa] baafaman irraa taata.”"
  26,168,"[Luuxis] ni jedhe: “Dhugumatti, ani namoota dalagaa keessan jibban irraayyi"
  26,169,Yaa Gooftaa kiyya! Anaafi maatii kiyya waan isaan dalagan irraa nu baraari.”
  26,170,Isaafi maatii isaas walumaa galatti ni baraarsine
  26,171,"Jaartii tokko kan warra [adaba keessatti] hafan irraa taate malee"
  26,172,Ergasii warra biroo ni balleessine
  26,173,"Bokkaa [adabbii] isaan irratti roobsineRoobni warra akeekkachiifamanii waa fokkate"
  26,174,"Dhugumatti, kana keessa mallattootu jiraIrra hedduun isaaniis Mu’uminoota hin taane"
  26,175,"Dhugumatti Gooftaan kee Isatu injifataa, rahmata godhaadha"